Description: ==============
        Flask-Graphite
        ==============
        
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/flask_graphite.svg
                :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/flask_graphite
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/github/license/numberly/mongo-thingy.svg
